Firaministan Indiya zai halarci bikin gina haikalin a wurin da ake takaddama
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin kafa wani haikalin Hindu a wata wata mai zuwa a wani wuri mai rikici a arewacin Indiya inda 'yan Hindu masu tsattsauran ra'ayi suka rushe masallacin karni na 16 a shekarar 1992, a cewar amintaccen wanda ke kula da ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya taron suka ce ta kasance mai kyau ga 'yan Hindu amma kuma ta kasance shekara guda tun lokacin da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin mulkin kai na jihar da ke da Musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Ba zai yiwu a manta da alamomin ba ga magoya baya da kuma masu adawa da jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata ta Modi, ko BJP, wacce ta nuna aniyar kawar da mulkin kai na Kashmir da ke fama da rikici da kuma gina haikalin allahn Hindu Ram a inda masallacin Mughal ya kasance, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu bi suka yi imanin cewa wurin haihuwar Ram ne.
Saboda cutar coronavirus har yanzu tana ta yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wacce ta ba da rahoton mafi girman adadin mutane a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye a talabijin na jihar kuma za a iyakance yawan mahalarta da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "mahimmin cibiyar jituwa ta zamantakewa, haɗin kan ƙasa da haɗin kai da farkawar jin daɗin Hindutva", ko hanyar rayuwar Hindu, mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar Vinod Bansal ya ce a cikin sanarwar manema labarai a ranar Asabar.
An warware takaddama ta tsawon karni game da shafin a shekarar da ta gabata bayan nasarar zaben BJP.
