Tsaron da aka tsaurara a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
Akwai tsananin tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu, China ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka ke shirin barin harabar.
An ga manyan motoci uku suna shiga cikin ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda masu saka tufafi da farar hula suka yi layi a bangarorin biyu na titin, waɗanda aka yi wa katanga da katanga.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta kasar Sin ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu sa'o'i 72 don rufewa, ko har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga watan Yuli.
China ta zargi wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu da "yin ayyukan da ba su dace da asalinsu ba".
Ba tare da bayar da wani bayani ba, kakakin ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya tsoma baki a harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da bukatun tsaro.
An bayar da umarnin kasar Sin ta rufe ofishin jakadancin a Chengdu a ranar Juma'a a matsayin ramuwar gayya ga umarnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare dukiyar ilimi ta Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurkawa".
Yayin da aka rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu mutane da suka bayyana a matsayin jami'an Amurka suna kutsawa cikin ginin ta kofar baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa ya keta yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da ta biyu kuma China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da bayyana yadda ba.
Rufewar ido-da-ido ya kara tsananta tashin hankali tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan da suka shafi kasuwanci da leken asiri na masana'antu zuwa hakkin dan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban 'yan ta'addan Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD -- Rahoton Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce 'yan tawaye 'yan Pakistan sama da 6,000 ne ke buya a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka haramta da ke da alhakin kai hare-hare kan sojojin Pakistan da fararen hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta haɗu da reshen kungiyar ta Islamic State da ke Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan TTP sun ma shiga kungiyar IS, wacce ke da hedikwata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa ranar Lahadi ba ga buƙatun The Associated Press don yin sharhi.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, wanda aka sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, an yi mummunan hari da sojojin tsaron Afghanistan da kuma sojojin Amurka da NATO, har ma a wasu lokuta da Taliban na Afghanistan.
Kungiyar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke lura da takunkumi da kuma bincike, wadda ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a fadin duniya, ce ta shirya rahoton.
Rahoton ya kiyasta membobin IS a Afghanistan a 2,200, kuma yayin da jagorancinsa ya ragu, IS har yanzu yana ƙidaya a cikin shugabannin 'yan ƙasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar sa ido ta samu bayanai cewa manyan kwamandojin kungiyar IS guda biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan kwanan nan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Duk da cewa a yankin da suke, (Kungiyar ta Islama) na iya kai hare-hare masu tsanani a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakanan yana da nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban waɗanda ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka, "in ji rahoton, yana mai nuni da yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta sanya hannu tare da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An cimma wannan yarjejeniya ne domin baiwa Amurka damar kawo karshen shafe shekaru 19 tana aiki a Afghanistan, kuma ta bukaci Taliban ta tabbatar da cewa kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda ba za su yi amfani da yankinta ba.
Ana sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta kuma tabbatar da cikakken shiga hannun Taliban a yaki da IS.
Sashe na biyu kuma mai yiwuwa mafi mahimmanci na yarjejeniyar yana kira ga tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabannin siyasar Kabul.
A daren Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa da ke cewa wakilin zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake tafiya ta yankin yana neman fara tattaunawar, wanda aka dage shi sau da yawa yayin da bangarorin biyu ke rikici kan shirin sakin fursunoni.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ta goyi bayan ta bukaci gwamnatin Afghanistan ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 kuma Taliban ta saki ma'aikatan gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira nuna kyakkyawar niyya kafin tattaunawar.
Har zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunonin Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira manyan masu laifi kuma ta ba da kyauta kyauta.
'Yan Taliban sun ki.
"Jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar tsakanin kasashen Afghanistan, babban mataki na gaba don kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na shekaru 40", in ji sanarwar Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka.
"Ko da yake an samu ci gaba sosai wajen musayar fursunoni, batun na bukatar karin ƙoƙari don warware shi gaba ɗaya".
Kakakin siyasar Taliban a farkon wannan makon ya ce a shirye yake ya yi tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan bikin Islama na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan, idan aka kammala sakin fursunonin.
Babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shine kasancewar mayakan a Afghanistan, musamman masu alaka da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke tare da Baluchistan Liberation Army, wanda ya dauki alhakin manyan hare-hare a wannan watan a lardin Sindh da ke kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe wasu jami'an sojin Pakistan a wannan watan a lardin Baluchistan da ke kudu maso yammacin kasar a yakin da suka yi da 'yan tawaye.
TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin munanan hare-haren da aka kai a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kai hari kan wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan kuma aka kashe mutane 140.
Yawancin su ɗalibai ne, wasu kuma 'yan shekara biyar.
"Adadin 'yan ta'addan Pakistan da ke Afghanistan, wadanda ke barazana ga kasashen biyu, an kiyasta su tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, mafi yawansu suna da TTP", in ji rahoton.
