SEATTLE - Bayan makonni na tashin hankali tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Oregon, mutane kusan 2,000 sun taru a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a tituna kuma suna gwagwarmaya da 'yan sanda.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar a asibiti da rauni a kafa da fashewar ya haifar, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 tun da yamma, in ji 'yan sanda.
Dauke da alamun kamar "Feds Go Home" da kuma ihu "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya", masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da za a kafa cibiyar tsare matasa kuma sun ƙone gine-gine a can.
Wasu windows da aka fasa na kasuwancin da ke kusa.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci taron jama'a a unguwar Capitol Hill, suna amfani da bama-bamai da kuma feshin barkono kafin su fara kama mutane.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekara 52, daga Kirkland, Washington, ta ce tana zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce ta damu da ganin irin wannan mummunan aiki da 'yan sanda ke yi.
"Wannan ba ƙasar da na yi ƙaura zuwa ba", in ji Ms. Mukherjee, wadda ta zo daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka shige.
"Ina jin kamar muna saurin zama jihar 'yan sanda da ta'addanci".
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar ta shafi hukumomin gari da kuma tura jami'an tarayya wadanda suka fara murkushe zanga-zangar da aka dade ana yi a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dabarun tilasta yin doka a Portland, wanda ya hada da amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye da kuma bindigogi masu sarrafa jama'a, suna da hatsari da rashin dacewa.
"Wannan mummunan abu ne mai tsanani", in ji Mr. Savage yayin da yake wanke idanunsa da man shafawa da kuma kula da rauni a hannunsa daga wani bam.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ya haifar da zanga-zangar da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane zuwa kan tituna a birane da dama, amma waɗannan zanga-zangar sun ragu a yawancin biranen.
Seattle da Portland, duk da haka, sun ga zanga-zangar da aka tsawaita.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle a wani lokaci sun yi ikirarin mallakar gidaje da yawa na unguwar Capitol Hill kuma sun ayyana yankin mai cin gashin kansa.
Bayan jerin harbe-harben da aka yi a can ya sa 'yan sanda suka share yankin, zanga-zangar ta lafa.
A halin yanzu, Portland, ta ci gaba da zanga-zanga, tare da wasu daga cikin zanga-zangar da ta fi tsanani a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a birnin.
Bayan Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutummutumai da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Cikin Gida ta tura ƙungiyoyin dabaru zuwa garin, ta fara jerin rikice-rikicen da suka haifar da masu zanga-zangar da suka ji rauni, binciken babban sufeto da kuma kiran daga shugabannin gida don jami'an tarayya su bar.
Mutane da yawa da suka yi zanga-zanga a birnin sun ƙaru zuwa dubbai, kuma zanga-zangar ta ci gaba.
A wannan makon, jami'an tarayya sun tura wata tawagar dabaru zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun ambaci wannan ci gaban a matsayin daya daga cikin dalilan zanga-zangar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar Portland ta kasance a tsakiyar gari, zanga-zangar ranar Asabar ta yi yawo a yankunan da ke gabashin tsakiyar gari, inda kotun tarayya ta birnin take.
