Magajin garin Kansas City ya yi maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen warware kisan kai, amma yana damuwa da muradin Trump
Magajin garin Kansas City Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi game da dalilan Shugaba Trump na aika jami'an tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimako wajen warware jerin laifukan kisan kai a cikin garin Midwestern, yana ganin matakin na iya zama game da ƙarfafa damar sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci motsin Black Lives Matter", Lucas, dan Democrat, ya ce a "Fox News Sunday" na zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da rashin daidaiton launin fata da zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka lamarin yake ba a Kansas City. Mun sami ƙaruwa kowace shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kai shi ne a kawar da wasu kashe-kashen da ba a warware ba".
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin samun takamaiman kuma mai da hankali kan warware kisan kai... Ina ganin idan kun saurari bayanan kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tarayya a cikin iyakantaccen yanki".
Duk da shirye-shiryensa na sanya jami'an tarayya suyi aiki tare da tilasta bin doka a cikin gida, Lucas ya ce maganganun Trump - musamman dangane da gardamar da ke kewaye da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Oregon - ya sa yawancin masu zaɓensa su nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a titunan birni.
"Abin da ba mu buƙatar ƙarin man fetur a kan wuta daga jami'an tarayya don yin, ina tsammanin, batun siyasa mai ban sha'awa", in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance karuwar yawan wasu laifuka - matakin da ke nuna fadada sa hannun Fadar White House a cikin tilasta bin doka a cikin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "doka da tsari".
"Taron" jami'an da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka wani bangare ne na Operation Legend - wanda aka sanya wa sunan bayan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka harbe shi da bindiga yayin da yake barci a wani gida a Kansas City a ƙarshen watan da ya gabata.
Duk da cewa aika jami'an tarayya don taimakawa tilasta bin doka a cikin gida ba sabon abu bane - Babban Lauyan Bill Barr ya ba da sanarwar irin wannan yunƙurin a watan Disamba don birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - nau'in jami'an tarayya da aka aika, da wasu dabarun su, sun haifar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisa na jihohi da na gida.
Wasu 'yan majalisa daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana game da gwamnatin Trump da ke aika da jami'an zuwa garuruwansu, musamman bayan rahotanni cewa jami'an tarayya da ba a san su ba sun kama masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun dauke su cikin motocin da ba a yi musu alama ba.
Portland ta sha fama da zanga-zangar kusan kowace rana game da zaluncin 'yan sanda da wariyar launin fata tun mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
