Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakatariyar fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwar kafofin yada labarai ta hanyar sanya jawabinta na siyasa maimakon na bayanai - a bayyane ya manta cewa 'yan jarida suna zabar tambayoyin.
Wani labarin Asabar da AP, babbar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Amurka, ya ce taron manema labarai na Fadar White House na iya zama "al'adar da ta lalace", kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "mai daidaitawa, cikakken talla ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zaɓe, wurin kai hari kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ba shi da haske game da bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
Wannan na ƙarshe ba za a iya musanta shi ba, domin babu sabon bayani da aka bayyana a taron.
Abin da AP ta manta da shi shi ne cewa kusan babu wani sabon bayani da ake nema a taron.
Masu rahoto suna amfani da matattarar fadar White House don jawo hankali ga kansu, wani nau'i na fasaha wanda Jim Acosta na CNN ya kammala.
Sun wuce dangantakar da ke tsakanin kafofin watsa labarai da gwamnati, suna maimaita juna wajen yin tambayoyi da suka shafi shugaban kasa Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna sanya kansu cikin labarai, kamar lokacin da wakilin CBS News Weijia Jiang ya amsa tambayar "Tambaya China" daga Trump ta hanyar yin wani abu mai ban mamaki game da wariyar launin fata: "Malam, me yasa kake fada min hakan?"
Wani taron tattaunawa na ranar 6 ga watan Yuli ya ba da babban misali na katsewar yadda taron tattaunawa ya daina zama tushen bayanai masu ma'ana ga Amurkawa.
Trump ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an lalata kallon talabijin na NASCAR ta hanyar zargin karya game da aikata laifi na ƙiyayya a kan direba Bubba Wallace da kuma yanke shawarar hana nuna tutar Confederate a abubuwan da suka faru.
Kamar yadda aka zata, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet kamar yadda mai ba da rahoto bayan mai ba da rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyi da aka tsara don sa ta ce Trump yana goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany ba ta bayar da amsar da 'yan jarida ke so ba - wata murya mai zafi da za ta cutar da Trump - amma ta amsa ta maimaitawa ta hanyar cewa shugaban ba ya ɗaukar matsayi game da tutar Confederate kuma ainihin saƙonsa shi ne cewa ana nuna masu sha'awar NASCAR ba daidai ba a matsayin wariyar launin fata.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya ce ta yi sauti "mai fushi" a lokacin taron.
Labarin AP ya yi daidai da wani shafi na Washington Post a farkon wannan watan da mai ba da rahoto na ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shine shugaban kungiyar wakilan fadar White House.
Karl ya yi jayayya, "ƙin yarda da gaskiyar da kuma amfani da fage na Fadar White House don dalilai na siyasa ne kawai ya sabawa amincewar jama'a".
Duk da haka, hanzarin McEnany da salon gwagwarmayar da ta yi ya sa ta zama jaruma ga wasu magoya bayan Trump, tun lokacin da ta ba da jawabinta na farko a ranar 1 ga Mayu bayan ta zama sakataren yada labarai a watan Afrilu.
