Wannan canji ya zo daga bangarorin biyu kuma ya riga ya zo kafin zuwan McEnany.
Wani gasa da aka yi wa tsohon sakataren yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders da 'yar wasan kwaikwayo Michelle Wolf a gidan cin abincin White House Correspondents a watan Afrilun 2018 ya kasance mai ban tsoro har ma da mai gabatar da MSNBC Mika Brzezinski ya kira shi "abin kunya".
Wakilin gidan farin na AP Jill Colvin ta gaishe McEnany a taron farko ta hanyar tambaya, "Za ku yi alkawarin ba za ku taɓa yi mana ƙarya daga wannan podium ba?"
