Ted Cruz ya ce manufar Pelosi ita ce "taɗa kuɗi a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanatan Republican Ted Cruz na Texas ya zargi Kakakin Majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da 'yan Democrat na Majalisar da tura wani kunshin agaji na cutar coronavirus wanda ya mai da hankali kan "sanya kudi kan matsalar da rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan matakin na gaba.
A wata hira da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar rikice-rikice biyu a lokaci guda: annobar duniya da ta lakume rayukan mutane sama da 600,000 a duk duniya da kuma "matsanancin bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a "Face the Nation" gaban sanatan, "ba a mayar da hankali kan ko ɗaya daga cikin waɗannan ba".
"Manufarta ita ce ta tara kudi a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka", in ji Jam'iyyar Republican ta Texas.
"Kuma musamman, idan ka kalli kudaden dala tiriliyan 3 da take kokarin turawa, kawai tana karkatar da kudi ga abokanta ne ba don magance matsalar ba.
'Yan majalisar dattijai na Republican da Fadar White House sun shafe makon da ya gabata suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan mataki na hudu na maganin coronavirus, wanda suke tsammanin zai ci dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows da sakataren baitulmalin Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don kara tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattijai, kuma Mnuchin ya fadawa Fox News a wata hira da ta yi a ranar Lahadi cewa shugaban majalisar dattijai Mitch McConnell ne zai bayyana cikakkun bayanai a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi damun 'yan majalisa - kuma batun takaddama tsakanin 'yan Republican da' yan Democrat - shine karewar karin kudaden rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara fita a karshen wannan makon.
Yayin da 'yan Democrat ke son kunshin "lokaci na huɗu" na coronavirus don ci gaba da haɓaka $ 600 zuwa fa'idodi, 'yan Republican suna kira da a rage shi kuma suna jayayya cewa wasu Amurkawa suna samun ƙarin daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke karbar karin albashin rashin aikin yi ana biyan su fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce ya yi magana da kananan masu kasuwanci a Texas wadanda ke da matsalar sake daukar ma'aikata.
"Tabbas, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyansu, a wasu lokuta, sau biyu na kudi don su zauna a gida", in ji shi.
Cruz ya ce ya kamata Majalisa ta mai da hankali kan zartar da dokar farfadowa da za ta sauƙaƙa wa Amurkawa komawa aiki ta hanyar sassauta haraji da ƙa'idodi kan ƙananan kamfanoni: "maimakon kawai fitar da tiriliyan daga ƙofar, dokar farfadowa za ta dakatar da harajin albashi, wanda zai ba da ƙarin albashi ga kowa a Amurka wanda ke aiki. Wannan a zahiri yana dawo da mutane aiki, "in ji shi.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata cewa shirin taimakon na gaba ya hada da rage harajin albashi, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai zama wani bangare na dokar ba, saboda ba a karɓi wannan shawarar ba a tsakanin 'yan Republican.
Mista Trump ya amince da cewa rage harajin albashi ba zai kasance a cikin lissafin na gaba ba amma ya nemi ya dora laifin a kan 'yan Democrat.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya yi hamayya da kudin kunshin na gaba, ya ce a ranar Lahadi ba ya cikin jirgin tare da matakin daga 'yan majalisa na majalisa.
Amma kuma ya soki kudurin dala tiriliyan 3 da majalisar wakilai ta Democrats ta zartar a watan Mayu kuma ya zargi abokan adawarsa da shirya wani mataki da zai cutar da shugaban kasar kafin zaben Nuwamba.
"Manufar da 'yan Democrat ke da ita ita ce ta kayar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar rashin amincewa da mafi kyawun hanyar da za su kayar da Donald Trump ita ce rufe kowane kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowane makaranta a Amurka", in ji shi.
"Ka sani, Nancy Pelosi tana magana ne game da maza da mata masu aiki. Abin da ta ke ba da shawara shi ne hana maza da mata masu aiki aiki".
