Rahul Gandhi Ya Zuwa Ga Jama'a Kan Batun Rajasthan
Jam'iyyar Congress Rahul Gandhi ta wallafa wani bidiyo a shafinta na Twitter a yau tana kokarin tara mutane kan BJP kan abubuwan da suka faru a Rajasthan.
Ta amfani da hashtag #SpeakUpForDemocracy, post dinsa na Hindi ya bukaci mutane da su "haɗa kai da ɗaga muryarmu don dimokiradiyya".
Jam'iyyar ta shirya zanga-zangar a duk fadin kasar a ranar Litinin kan halin da ake ciki a jihar Rajasthan, inda gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot ke fama da rayuwa.
A yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a gudanar da zanga-zanga a wajen fadar Shugaban kasa, gidan shugaban kasar Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, Jam'iyyar ta zargi jam'iyyar BJP da "karye kundin tsarin mulki da rusa dimokiradiyya" yayin da duk kasar ke yaki da cutar coronavirus.
Ya yi haka a Madhya Pradesh, in ji jam'iyyar.
"Muna bukatar a kira taron majalisa nan take wanda ya dace da hakkokinmu na kundin tsarin mulki", jam'iyyar ta ce a bidiyon.
Gwamnan jihar Rajasthan Kalraj Mishra ya ki amincewa da wata shawara ta fara zaman majalisar.
An gabatar da na biyu a yau wanda ya ce yana nazari.
