Tun da farko a yau, Ministan Tsaro Rajnath Singh, Ministansa Shripad Naik, Shugaban Ma'aikatan Tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, Shugaban Sojoji Janar M M Naravane, Shugaban Sojojin Sama Marshal R K S Bhadauria da Shugaban Sojojin Ruwa Admiral Karambir Singh suma sun ba da girmamawa a Amar Jawan Jyoti a National War Memorial.
